## Debugging
- Use structured logging with context (structlog recommended).
- Include correlation IDs in all log entries.
- Log at appropriate levels: ERROR for failures, INFO for key events.

## Troubleshooting
- Check security shield logs first when content is blocked.
- Verify GCP credentials are valid and not expired.
- Review Model Armor templates for false positives.